Nearly 100 golfers participated in the Polokwa ne Golf Club s club day hosted on Saturday followed by a social day on Sunday. Julius Mapatha and Sipho Talane top scored with 76 points leaving second place on the podium to Adam Milanzi and Thabo Shingange with 71 points. Charlie and Lynette Smith claimed were third on 67 points. Gavin Stanford and Duncan Menzies claimed the prizes for nearest to the pin on the fourth and 16th hole respectively. Golfers are reminded that the club will be open on Friday and another club day will be hosted on Saturday. Story and photos: RC Myburgh &gt;&gt;rc.observer@gmail.com Featured photo: Joas Legodi prepares to putt. Andries du Plessis lines up his ball with the hole.